Class WingsEndpoint.LinkEvent

    WingsEndpoint

    public abstract static class WingsEndpoint.LinkEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class of an event emitted when the link state of an endpoint changes. The event is also emitted to a subscriber immediately after subscription.
